rc/main/java/com/example/order/web/OrderApiController.java: REST API controller\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Spring Boot config\n- src/main/resources/templates/order.html: Thymeleaf template (replaces order.xhtml)\n- src/main/resources/templates/lineItem.html: Thymeleaf template (replaces lineItem.xhtml)\n- src/main/resources/static/css/default.css: Stylesheet\n- smoke.py: 12 smoke tests\n- CHANGELOG.md: Migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/java/jakarta/ (entire old package tree with 8 Java files)\n- src/main/liberty/ (Open Liberty server.xml)\n- src/main/webapp/ (JSF XHTML templates, web.xml, CSS resources)\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml\n```\n\n### Test Results\n```\nResults: 12 passed, 0 failed, 12 total\n```\n\n### Error Handling\n- **Error Summary:** 0 errors encountered during migration\n- **Critical Issues:** None\n- **Manual Intervention Required:** None"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":526,"cache_read_input_tokens":106442,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":526,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":853},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e2b0509a-15a6-43ee-b7b2-9e48288140b4","uuid":"28126be1-4ae4-4a2a-a2e9-1862d4ba0c1e"}
